TopicTitle: Expedition-I rocket / land on duna and return with science / No boosters

Articles.Content:
I'm just showing off my rocket I made/used to go to duna, land, collect science and return to kerbin.

I flew it, mission was success with no problems.

I do use FAR and DRE btw.

And also this used stock parts only.
